	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Making an adjustment</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the Select button. A window will appear.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Select employee(s) and click on the Select button.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Select a leave type.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">4.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Insert number of day(s) to be added/deducted from the selected employee's leave entitlment. (to deduct, just add a minus "-" infront of the number).</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">5.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Insert the reason.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">6.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the Submit button to submit the leave application for approval.</td>
